# 📚 Bookstore API

A production-ready RESTful API for an online bookstore built with Django and Django REST Framework.

The project provides secure phone number authentication using One-Time Passwords (OTP), JWT-based authorization, shopping cart management, payment gateway integration, and interactive API documentation.

---

## ✨ Features

- 🔐 Phone number authentication (OTP)
- 🔑 JWT authentication
- 👤 User profile management
- 📚 Book catalog
- 🛒 Shopping cart
- 💳 Payment gateway integration (Zarinpal)
- 📄 Swagger & ReDoc API documentation
- 🐳 Docker support
- 📦 RESTful API
- 🔍 Filtering and pagination

---

## 🛠 Tech Stack

- Python 3.12
- Django 6
- Django REST Framework
- JWT Authentication
- SQLite (Development)
- PostgreSQL (Docker / Production)
- Docker & Docker Compose
- Kavenegar SMS API
- Zarinpal Payment Gateway
- Swagger (drf-yasg)

