### Directory Overview

| Directory | Description |
|------------|-------------|
| **apps/** | Contains all Django applications following a modular architecture. |
| **accounts/** | User authentication, OTP login, JWT authentication, and profile management. |
| **books/** | Book catalog and related business logic. |
| **cart/** | Shopping cart functionality. |
| **payments/** | Payment processing and gateway integration. |
| **bookstore_backend/settings/** | Environment-specific Django settings (base, development, production). |
| **media/** | Uploaded media files. |
| **Dockerfile** | Docker image definition. |
| **docker-compose.yml** | Multi-container Docker configuration. |
| **requirements.txt** | Python project dependencies. |
| **API_DOCS.txt** | API documentation notes. |


