## 🔑 Authentication Flow

1. Register using a phone number
2. Request an OTP code
3. Verify the OTP
4. Receive JWT Access & Refresh Tokens
5. Authenticate future requests using:

```
Authorization: Bearer <access_token>
```

---

## 📌 Main API Endpoints

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|---------|----------|-------------|
| POST | `/api/accounts/register/` | Register a new user |
| POST | `/api/accounts/send-otp/` | Request an OTP |
| POST | `/api/accounts/verify-otp/` | Verify OTP |
| GET | `/api/accounts/profile/` | Retrieve user profile |
| PATCH | `/api/accounts/profile/` | Update user profile |

